Re: I have a question about the Yoon and Dakuten/Handakuten
by phreadom » Sat 12.17.2011 7:30 am You most definitely do need to learn them. It would be like telling you that you don't need to learn half of the English alphabet. You'd be totally lost when you tried to read anything. Is there some particular part of learning them that is confusing to you?http://thejapanesepage.com/beginners/hi ... mbinationshttp://thejapanesepage.com/beginners/hi ... nationstwohttp://thejapanesepage.com/beginners/hiragana/SmallTsuRead those over and ask if there is some part of that you're having trouble with and we can try to work through it. 猿も木から落ちる
