Re: I have a question about the Yoon and Dakuten/Handakuten
by Hyperworm » Sat 12.17.2011 11:03 am That's chouon(pu) （長音符）By yoon I think we're talking about 拗音（ようおん）.[edit: I didn't know the term before this. Normally I call them glides. .-.]
